<!-- ============= Introduction ============================== -->
  <sect1 id="gcalc-introduction"> 
	 <title>Introduction</title> 
	 <para><application>GNOME Calculator</application> is a simple mathematical
		and scientific calculator that includes arithmetic, trigonometric, and
		logarithmic functions.</para> 
	 <para>To start <application>&app;</application>, open the <guimenu>Applications</guimenu> menu on the Menu Panel, then choose 
		<menuchoice> 
		  <guisubmenu>Accessories</guisubmenu> 
		  <guimenuitem>Calculator</guimenuitem> 
		</menuchoice>. </para> 
	 <para>When you start <application>&app;</application>, the
		<application>&app;</application> window is displayed.</para>
