		  the next number that you enter. When you click on <guibutton>EE</guibutton>,
		  the calculator displays e+ in the display field to represent 10 to the power of
		  the next number that you enter. For example, if you enter 5, 
		  <guibutton>EE</guibutton>, 2, <guibutton>=</guibutton>, the calculator displays
